Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个白痴  别装模作样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的话  你先生会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  随孩子他妈…高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  差不多了  你还是阻止下她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈  原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫札克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫札克？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  莫札克？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  被你抛弃的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫札克将军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候还只有这么小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫札  莫札…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这么小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  听莫札克的  就原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈  还是没原谅老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我也花心过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和弹珠店的小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去卡拉OK吧  去吧  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个弹珠店的店员就是我大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥之前对我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个爆炸头的粗鲁大妈在搞我  好伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要从那家弹珠店辞职呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么的好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他爸  我们也跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦  孩子他妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫札克  你也来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法少女恭子  我们也跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在店门前跳什么土风舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住这个机会  打倒魔法少女恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫札克！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烫　烫烫烫烫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫札克！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫札克！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么都烧了解决
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆热少女  魔法少女恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此这般  魔法少女恭子为了保护地球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也和恶势力进行了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  魔法少女恭子  这周也让我好感动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人专用旅馆「结城亭」即将开放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想试着做一次旅馆的老板娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那么简单就能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且你要建在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.67,0:23:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心  我在旧校舍建好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:23:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就只要等客人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.55,0:23:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  就拜托你招揽客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.13,0:23:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招揽客人?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:23:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人  很便宜哦  很便宜哦  来住一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜到一夜一千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  To  LOVEる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.18,0:24:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结城亭血风录
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.40,0:24:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果来到地球  请您一定光临
